{"tid":1466293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[所有人入]立即停止機場捉鬼行動","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:39:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T02:39:30.000Z","uid":65790,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2135bdbd8648aba8eb334c85417723b68a935ca6","tid":1466293,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:39:09.000Z","msg":"就算有中國人係度又點? 佢都有自由係機場<br />\n我地係機場只係和平集會去癱瘓機場<br />\n就算有所謂&quot;鬼&quot;亦都唔會影響我地行動<br />\n黑警亦都唔會夠膽拉人<br />\n<br />\n根本係機場捉鬼根本冇意思<br />\n俾你捉到你又可以做咩? <br />\n反而如果你捉錯人就會係核彈黎<br />\n<br />\n機場行動本身和理非力量係最大最有效<br />\n勇武派一定要BACK UP和理非完成行動<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8771a6e4e9e33223b56f48c17e32c54ce62462e1","tid":1466293,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:47:10.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfede0e453e6962c575b98ea4e2b9c2aa875bef1","tid":1466293,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:50:02.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4138df187ab00f319fec014dc632a3ac4bd6339f","tid":1466293,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:53:55.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"316ad23e313cd330d1ed37781a50e50bee81c503","tid":1466293,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:55:54.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf0c33705f648c1454477f3d3d1939894501184d","tid":1466293,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:56:38.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7748dc3c13bfc914ceaea469b6d0c67002945b6a","tid":1466293,"uid":36920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:57:13.000Z","msg":"對場運動嚟講<br />\n打救護同打立場其實仲大穫過放核彈"},{"pid":"4836d8beffe40b491d7a1e4f60052f0b3ca75587","tid":1466293,"uid":65790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7748dc3c13bfc914ceaea469b6d0c67002945b6a","tid":1466293,"uid":36920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:57:13.000Z","msg":"對場運動嚟講<br />\n打救護同打立場其實仲大穫過放核彈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:01:54.000Z","msg":"你話唔係鬼冇人信<br />\n前線係勇武但唔係無腦<br />\n<br />\n我地呢場運動最大既朋友就係救護同記者<br />\n點會搞佢地<br />\n<br />\n邊個搞事, 真勇武一定要制止同控制場面<br />\n機場無需要捉鬼!"},{"pid":"83db2235a81f320e8817a87312c2a5e8051159d3","tid":1466293,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:02:53.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eca27d29b41d11dfc0312e32bb2ecb008a22aec1","tid":1466293,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:04:27.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a78709bcd2c30dbbba0cfd3f3bd5b44f07670245","tid":1466293,"uid":292067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:05:28.000Z","msg":"我係何妖實恥笑<br />\n我由頭到尾無割過 無被割過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地班撚樣 少少野都割又分化<br />\n<br />\n派只共狗比你地你地完好無缺放走佢 仲要比人影哂先放人 多謝哂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b9a3adde5dedf203e82f1322cb5f8767fd48989","tid":1466293,"uid":111694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:05:31.000Z","msg":"［中計撚入］唔好成日話輸民心啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466381\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466381</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"653ec20377ddeff2d2190db8dad0f1f933fa74bd","tid":1466293,"uid":42554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:05:32.000Z","msg":"唔完美，可接受，但可以改善同改進<br />\n<br />\n不捉鬼"},{"pid":"a8a5ba3e1b59a46219307f589e48ce12e682cbe6","tid":1466293,"uid":78255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:05:54.000Z","msg":"鬼一定有 和理非場合最應該做嘅係冷處理<br />\n冇人理捉鬼就唔會搞咁大件事<br />\n我地入機場唔係為咗捉鬼 要記得呢樣野"},{"pid":"8ab451f9db8ca15c3437ce8414ab9549837d93f4","tid":1466293,"uid":74869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:06:09.000Z","msg":"其實佢請幾十個普通人著黑衫 捉一個預定俾佢捉既鬼<br />\n就可以帶動成個機場既風向 同連登分化 <br />\n我地要做既係和理非現場停止捉鬼 因為對我地無害性<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 利申 不割 做左就做左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07805c0ab5f85927c52c5b4150648849c15f7eff","tid":1466293,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:07:39.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09ed16f4c72f043fe031fe10d827396edd6a193e","tid":1466293,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ab451f9db8ca15c3437ce8414ab9549837d93f4","tid":1466293,"uid":74869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:06:09.000Z","msg":"其實佢請幾十個普通人著黑衫 捉一個預定俾佢捉既鬼<br />\n就可以帶動成個機場既風向 同連登分化 <br />\n我地要做既係和理非現場停止捉鬼 因為對我地無害性<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 利申 不割 做左就做左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:09:29.000Z","msg":"不割就梗架啦<br />\n但捉鬼呢個行為會影響到成件事<br />\n所有人唔捉鬼就冇事<br />\n<br />\n邊個捉鬼其實都係鬼<br />\n機場完全冇需要捉鬼<br />\n行動完全公開, 就係和平集會, 捉鬼黎做咩?"},{"pid":"84843ce36cd57f3916ebe9e5c2072f520e0224d6","tid":1466293,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:11:33.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6b404375366c2268b514c242e975e77fc591bb8","tid":1466293,"uid":78255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09ed16f4c72f043fe031fe10d827396edd6a193e","tid":1466293,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote